---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/content.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="Switch to Modern Medical Equipment Planning Software | Estrelis.ai" description="Migrate your equipment planning data to Estrelis. Import projects, catalogs, and room assignments from any platform with AI-powered matching and validation.">

  <section class="content-hero">
    <h1>Moving from Another Platform?</h1>
    <p>Switching equipment planning tools doesn't mean starting over. Estrelis provides seamless data migration with AI-powered catalog matching to get your projects running on a modern platform.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Seamless Data Migration</h2>
    <p>Estrelis imports project data, equipment catalogs, room assignments, and budget information from your existing platform — whether it's spreadsheets, legacy planning software, or asset management systems. AI matches your existing equipment items to our catalog, identifies gaps, and flags items that need review.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Import project structures, rooms, and equipment lists from any source</li>
      <li>AI-powered catalog matching with confidence scores</li>
      <li>Automated identification of discontinued or changed items</li>
      <li>Budget and pricing data preserved during migration</li>
      <li>Historical project data retained for reference</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Why Teams Move to Estrelis</h2>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>AI-Native Platform</h3>
        <p>AI is woven into every workflow — from catalog management to spec matching to item generation. Not a feature add-on, but the core of how the platform works.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Modern Revit Integration</h3>
        <p>Direct two-way Revit plugin synchronization. No manual exports or imports — BIM data flows automatically between architectural models and equipment plans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Client Portal</h3>
        <p>Give healthcare clients passwordless access to review and approve equipment plans. No training required — stakeholders get magic link access.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Field Inventory</h3>
        <p>iPad-based field capture with 360° panoramic photos and AI asset identification. Data flows directly into project planning.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="related">
    <h3>Related</h3>
    <div class="related-links">
      <a href="/integrations/revit/">Revit Integration</a>
      <a href="/compare/spreadsheets/">vs Spreadsheets</a>
      <a href="/compare/traditional-planning/">vs Traditional Planning</a>
      <a href="/faq/">FAQ</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to modernize your equipment planning?</h2>
    <p>We'll help you migrate to Estrelis from any platform.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Request a Demo</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
